{"title":"Vue.js2.5+cube-ui重构饿了么App","date":"2020-05-20T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 20, 2020","L":"05/20/2020","MM-DD":"05-20"},"thumbnail":"https://blog-1251959181.file.myqcloud.com/cover/castle.jpg","link":"2020/05/20/vue-cube","comments":true,"tags":["Front-end","Note"],"categories":["Coding"],"updated":"2020-05-29T17:26:44.920Z","content":"<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.imooc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">慕课网</a>实战课程笔记 —— <a href=\"https://coding.imooc.com/class/74.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vue.js2.5+cube-ui重构饿了么App（经典再升级）</a></strong></p>\n<p>项目GitHub地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"项目准备工作\">项目准备工作<a title=\"#项目准备工作\" href=\"#项目准备工作\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1、vue-cli-3.0-介绍\">1、Vue-cli 3.0 介绍<a title=\"#1、vue-cli-3.0-介绍\" href=\"#1、vue-cli-3.0-介绍\"></a></h3>\n<p>Github地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vue-cli\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/vuejs/vue-cli</a><br>\n简体中文文档：<a href=\"https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/\" target=\"_blank\">https://cli.vuejs.org/zh/</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption><span>检查node与vue-cli版本并创建项目</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> node -v</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">v12.4.0</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> vue -V</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">@vue/cli 4.3.1</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> vue create vue-sell-cube</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>手动选择需要安装的依赖（上下键移动，空格选择/取消选择）\n<ul>\n<li><code>Babel</code></li>\n<li><code>CSS Pre-processors</code></li>\n<li><code>Linter / Formatter</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>预处理器：<code>Stylus</code></li>\n<li>ESLint规则：<code>Standard</code></li>\n<li>Lint规则：<code>Lint on save</code></li>\n<li>配置文件：<code>In dedicated config files</code></li>\n<li>是否保存预设：<code>n</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"2、目录介绍-&amp;-cube-ui-安装\">2、目录介绍 &amp; cube-ui 安装<a title=\"#2、目录介绍-&amp;-cube-ui-安装\" href=\"#2、目录介绍-&amp;-cube-ui-安装\"></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"项目目录\">项目目录<a title=\"#项目目录\" href=\"#项目目录\"></a></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>/node_moudules</li>\n<li>/public\n<ul>\n<li>favicon.ico</li>\n<li>index.html <em>入口html</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>/src <em>源文件</em>\n<ul>\n<li>/assets\n<ul>\n<li>logo.png</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>/cpmponents\n<ul>\n<li>HelloWorld.vue</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>App.vue</li>\n<li>main.js <em>入口JS</em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>babel.config.js</li>\n<li>package-lock.json</li>\n<li>package.json</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://README.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">README.md</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"安装cube-ui\">安装cube-ui<a title=\"#安装cube-ui\" href=\"#安装cube-ui\"></a></h4>\n<p>Github地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/didi/cube-ui\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/didi/cube-ui</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption><span>安装cube-ui插件</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> vue add cube-ui</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>是否使用后编译：<code>y</code></li>\n<li>导入类型：<code>Partly</code></li>\n<li>自定义主题：<code>y</code></li>\n<li>使用rem：<code>n</code></li>\n<li>使用vw：<code>n</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"3、api-接口-mock\">3、api 接口 mock<a title=\"#3、api-接口-mock\" href=\"#3、api-接口-mock\"></a></h3>\n<p>在 <a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell/blob/next/data.json\" target=\"_blank\">/data.json</a> 中写入模拟的数据，</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><figcaption><span>/vue.config.js</span><a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell/blob/next/vue.config.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> appData = <span class=\"built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"string\">'./data.json'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> seller = appData.seller</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> goods = appData.goods</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> ratings = appData.ratings</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">devServer: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    before(app) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      app.get(<span class=\"string\">'/api/seller'</span>, <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">req, res</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        res.json(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          errno: <span class=\"number\">0</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          data: seller</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      app.get(<span class=\"string\">'/api/goods'</span>, <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">req, res</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        res.json(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          errno: <span class=\"number\">0</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          data: goods</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      app.get(<span class=\"string\">'/api/ratings'</span>, <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">req, res</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        res.json(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          errno: <span class=\"number\">0</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">          data: ratings</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"头部组件开发\">头部组件开发<a title=\"#头部组件开发\" href=\"#头部组件开发\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"1、目录结构-&amp;-header-组件\">1、目录结构 &amp; header 组件<a title=\"#1、目录结构-&amp;-header-组件\" href=\"#1、目录结构-&amp;-header-组件\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>/src\n<ul>\n<li>/common\n<ul>\n<li>/stylus   样式文件</li>\n<li>/fonts    图标组件</li>\n<li>/js</li>\n<li>/mixins</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>/components\n<ul>\n<li>support-ico   图标组件</li>\n<li>v-header      头部组件</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>修改<code>meta</code>标签：<code>&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no&quot;&gt;</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"2、axios-封装-&amp;-数据获取\">2、axios 封装 &amp; 数据获取<a title=\"#2、axios-封装-&amp;-数据获取\" href=\"#2、axios-封装-&amp;-数据获取\"></a></h3>\n<p>axios: 易用、简洁且高效的http库</p>\n<p>Github地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/axios/axios\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/axios/axios</a></p>\n<p>axios中文网：<a href=\"http://www.axios-js.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.axios-js.com/</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption><span>安装axios</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">$</span><span class=\"bash\"> npm install axios --save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>把错误码的判断封装起来</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><figcaption><span>/src/api/helper.js</span><a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell/blob/next/src/api/helper.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> axios <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'axios'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> urlMap = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  development: <span class=\"string\">'/'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  production: <span class=\"string\">'http://ustbhuangyi.com/sell/'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> baseUrl = urlMap[process.env.NODE_ENV];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> ERR_OK = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">get</span>(<span class=\"params\">url</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"params\">params = &#123;&#125;</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> axios.get(baseUrl + url, &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      params</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;).then(<span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">res</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> &#123;errno, data&#125; = res.data;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (errno === ERR_OK) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> data</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;).catch(<span class=\"function\">(<span class=\"params\">e</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><figcaption><span>/src/api/index.js</span><a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell/blob/next/src/api/index.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> &#123; <span class=\"keyword\">get</span> &#125; from './helpers'</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">const getSeller = <span class=\"keyword\">get</span>('api/seller');</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">export &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  getSeller</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>封装以后<code>getSeller</code>方法一定能拿到数据</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>/src/App.vue</span><a href=\"https://github.com/ustbhuangyi/vue-sell/blob/next/src/App.vue\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;app&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;v-header :seller&#x3D;&quot;seller&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;v-header&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;&#x2F;template&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  import VHeader from &#39;components&#x2F;v-header&#x2F;v-header&#39;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  import &#123; getSeller &#125; from &#39;api&#39;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  export default &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    data() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      return &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        seller: &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    created() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      this._getSeller()</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    methods: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      _getSeller() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        getSeller().then((seller) &#x3D;&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">          this.seller &#x3D; seller</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    components: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      VHeader</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"3、header-detail-&amp;-star-组件\">3、header-detail &amp; star 组件<a title=\"#3、header-detail-&amp;-star-组件\" href=\"#3、header-detail-&amp;-star-组件\"></a></h3>\n<p>star组件封装了不同的贴图大小，进行四舍五入运算</p>\n<h3 id=\"4、header-detail-交互\">4、header-detail 交互<a title=\"#4、header-detail-交互\" href=\"#4、header-detail-交互\"></a></h3>\n<p>全屏弹窗放在<code>&lt;body&gt;</code>下最保险</p>\n<p>使用 cube-ui create-API 方法</p>\n<h2 id=\"tab-组件开发\">Tab 组件开发<a title=\"#tab-组件开发\" href=\"#tab-组件开发\"></a></h2>\n<!--\n\n### 1、tab 组件基础实现\n\n### 2、tab 组件上下联动\n\n### 3、tab 组件抽象和封装\n\n## 商品页面开发\n\n### 1、scroll-nav 组件应用\n\n### 2、shop-cart 组件\n\n### 3、cart-control 组件\n\n### 4、小球飞入动画实现\n\n### 5、侧边栏内容定制化\n\n### 6、购物车列表组件\n\n### 7、购物车 sticky 组件\n\n### 8、购物车列表功能完善\n\n### 9、弹层类组件优化\n\n## 商品详情页开发\n\n### 1、商品详情页骨架开发\n\n### 2、商品详情页购物开发\n\n### 3、商品详情页评价列表开发\n\n### 4、商品详情页评价选择组件开发\n\n## 评价和商家页面开发\n\n### 1、评价页面骨架开发和数据获取\n\n### 2、评价页面评价选择组件 mixin 抽取\n\n### 3、商家页面静态页面开发\n\n### 4、商家页面本地缓存封装实现\n\n## create-api 原理分析\n\n### 1、create-api 原理介绍\n\n### 2、create-api 源码分析（1）\n\n### 3、create-api 源码分析（2）\n\n### 4、create-api 源码分析（3）\n\n### 5、create-api 源码分析（4）\n\n## 打包构建和项目部署\n\n### 1、打包构建&性能优化\n\n### 2、搭建小型 node 服务代理接口\n\n### 3、部署到云服务器\n\n### 4、nginx 配置多项目部署方案 -->\n","prev":{"title":"Git 学习笔记","link":"2020/05/23/git"},"next":{"title":"“平安报”提醒服务自动化折腾日记","link":"2020/05/14/check-in"},"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2020/05/20/vue-cube/","toc":[{"id":"项目准备工作","title":"项目准备工作","index":"1","children":[{"id":"1、vue-cli-3.0-介绍","title":"1、Vue-cli 3.0 介绍","index":"1.1"},{"id":"2、目录介绍-&amp;-cube-ui-安装","title":"2、目录介绍 &amp; cube-ui 安装","index":"1.2"},{"id":"3、api-接口-mock","title":"3、api 接口 mock","index":"1.3"}]},{"id":"头部组件开发","title":"头部组件开发","index":"2","children":[{"id":"1、目录结构-&amp;-header-组件","title":"1、目录结构 &amp; header 组件","index":"2.1"},{"id":"2、axios-封装-&amp;-数据获取","title":"2、axios 封装 &amp; 数据获取","index":"2.2"},{"id":"3、header-detail-&amp;-star-组件","title":"3、header-detail &amp; star 组件","index":"2.3"},{"id":"4、header-detail-交互","title":"4、header-detail 交互","index":"2.4"}]},{"id":"tab-组件开发","title":"Tab 组件开发","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2020/05/20/vue-cube/\" title=\"Vue.js2.5+cube-ui重构饿了么App\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2020/05/20/vue-cube/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"May 20, 2020","updated":"May 29, 2020"}}